#code
t = int(input())
c = 1
while t>0:
 inp = [int(i) for i in input().split(' ')]
 m = inp[0]
 n = inp[1]
 inp = [int(i) for i in input().split(' ')]
 rx = inp[0]
 ry = inp[1]
 path_len = int(input())
 path = input()
 
 # print(path)
 posx = 0
 posy = 0
 for p in path:
  if p == 'L':
   posx -= 1
  elif p == 'R':
   posx += 1
  elif p == 'U':
   posy += 1
  elif p == 'D':
   posy -= 1
 
 if posx > m or posx < 0 or posy > n or posy < 0:
  print('Case ' + str(c) + ': ' + 'DANGER')
 elif posx != rx or posy != ry:
  print('Case ' + str(c) + ': ' + 'SOMEWHERE')
 elif posx == rx and posy == ry:
  print('Case ' + str(c) + ': ' + 'REACHED')
 t -= 1
 c += 1
